title: Florida city looks for answers after a 'zombie alert' was sent out
text: Florida city looks for answers after a 'zombie alert' was sent to residents 20 Hours Ago Officials say they still don't who sent a "zombie alert" to residents of a Florida city following a power outage. Lake Worth spokesman Ben Kerr says an independent investigation is underway to determine who was behind the message sent to some 7,880 customers during a 27-minute power outage Sunday.
